Subject: [PATCH 1/2] feat: comprehensive UI/UX overhaul - professional email
 templates, enhanced styling, improved views

PROFILE & SIDEBAR:
- Replaced broken flash messages with proper query-param toasts
- Added show/hide password toggles to all password fields
- Fixed avatar display in sidebar with image support
- Avatar camera overlay for quick uploads
- Improved profile info display (member since, email, role, etc)
- Sidebar user link is now clickable to /profile

EMAIL TEMPLATES:
- Rebuilt all 7 email templates with professional responsive HTML
- Per-email color themes (green=welcome, blue=verify, yellow=reset, etc)
- Beautiful gradient hero sections and info boxes
- Task assignment with context info
- Daily digest with overdue task lists
- Production-grade responsive layout wrapper

CSS & UI:
- Enhanced select/dropdown styling with custom chevron icons
- Priority colors with emoji icons ()
- Status colors with emoji icons ()
- Improved badge styling with borders
- Better form input hover/focus states
- Enhanced dropdown menus with rounded items
- Project cards with hover lift animation
- Password strength bar styling
- Better alert/flash message styles

VIEWS:
- Dashboard: greeting shows first name
- Project show: clearer Add Member UI with owner-only message
- Tasks: improved form styling and layout
- Layout: better favicon and branding

ROUTES:
- resolveWebUser now fetches avatar field
- renderWithLayout supports currentPath override
- Better flash/error message handling

140 tests passing (~71% coverage)
