 =?UTF-8?q?l,=20avatar,=20uploads,=20tests,=20missing=20routes?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

CRITICAL FIXES:
- Email: Rewrite isDevMode() → hasSmtpConfig(). Emails now actually send
  when EMAIL_HOST/USER/PASS are configured. Test mode = silent no-op.
  No more emails going to console.log when SMTP is set.
- Avatar URL: Use CLIENT_URL (not BASE_URL) consistently for avatar URLs.
  Normalize path separators for Windows compatibility.
- Uploads: Serve /uploads directory as static files so avatar images
  actually load in browser. Fixed app.ts to add express.static for uploads/.
- Email worker: taskAssigned now passes taskUrl. commentAdded now passes
  taskUrl. dailyDigest now passes task list for rendering in email body.

NEW API ROUTES (were missing entirely):
- GET  /api/projects        — list all projects with task counts
- GET  /api/projects/:id    — get project by ID
- DELETE /api/projects/:id  — delete project (owner only)
- POST /api/projects/:id/members         — add member (owner only)
- DELETE /api/projects/:id/members/:id   — remove member (owner only)
- DELETE /api/tasks/:id/comments/:id     — delete comment

CODE FIXES:
- Comment controller: accept both 'body' (spec) and 'content' (model) fields
- Comment validation: accept either 'body' or 'content' input field
- DigestEmailJob: add optional 'tasks' array for digest email body
- globalSetup: try multiple MongoDB versions; fallback to MONGODB_URI env var
- jest.config: increase testTimeout to 60s, serial execution, better coverage

NEW COMPREHENSIVE TESTS (26 new test files/additions):
- tests/unit/services/project.service.test.ts (new — 8 tests)
- tests/unit/services/comment.service.test.ts (new — 6 tests)
